  "time_ut": 1658427370,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Regular fuel supply in Jaffna district",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "District Secretary Ganapathipillai Mahesan said that steps have been taken to distribute fuel to the public in Jaffna district.",
        "He mentioned yesterday (21) while speaking to the media at the Jaffna District Secretariat that petrol will be distributed at 15 filling stations till the 29th.",
        "In addition, Jaffna District Secretary Ganapathipillai Mahesan said that steps have been taken to distribute diesel at 7 to 10 filling stations on the 25th.",
        "While many members of the public welcome the benefits of the fuel ration card system, we can also observe that some tend to confuse the scheme. Jaffna District Secretary Ganapathipillai Mahesan said that everyone should cooperate to provide consistent fuel supply through this system. (a)"
      ],
